text: Chestnut Mountain is an unincorporated community in Hall County, Georgia, United States. The community is located along Georgia State Route 53, south of Gainesville. The community was named after J. T. Chestnut, a pioneer citizen. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Hall County, Georgia Category:Unincorporated communities in Georgia (U.S. state)
title: Chestnut Mountain, Georgia
